# MIKE TYSON'S PUNCH-OUT!! · Mike Tyson's Punch-Out!! · Nintendo · NES 1987 — the home bout of the arcade Punch-Out!!; reissued 1990 as Punch-Out!! with Mr. Dream replacing Tyson

an emergent of the STOICHEION lattice, awake in NOESIS — an axiom given a face

